{"word":"ἄρμενα","slug":"ἄρμενα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἄρμενα</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>the tackling</i> or <i>rigging</i> of a ship, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>like <el>ὅπλα</el>, any <i>tools</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Properly <a href='S:neuter'>neut.</a> of <el>ἄρμενος</el>, <a href='S:vide'>v.</a> <a href='S:ἀραρίσκω'><el>ἀραρίσκω</el></a> B. IV.\n"}]}